  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Cyber Security Specialist (Lead)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Cyber Security Specialist (VAPT)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p>Architect, design, review and implement cyber security resilient in our product and projects. You are familiar with cloud security architectures and solutions, making sure the companies can operate in a safe, secure environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible in managing CyberSecurity VAPT, Vulnerability Assessment, Risk Management and Testing.</li>\n  <li>Manage Network and Cloud Security Risk Assessment and Audit.</li>\n  <li>Involved in handling Government Projects related to risk, security attacks and system solutions.</li>\n  <li>Consultancy on software and hardware for security vulnerabilities and risks</li>\n  <li>Plan VAPT, execution, result analysis and provide fix recommendation.</li>\n  <li>Provide guideline such as coding, key management, hardening, patch management, backup management, incident management, etc.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with IM8 requirements and CIS, NIST security benchmark, cyber security tools to perform preliminary scan.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Skills Required</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong in knowledge in CyberSecurity, Risk Assessment, VAPT, Vulnerability and Cloud Security.</li>\n  <li>Strong in VAPT management.</li>\n  <li>Technically incline in CyberSecurity, Cloud, Risk and Vulnerabilities.</li>\n  <li>Possess knowledge of IM8 and Government projects experience is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Degree/Certifications in CyberSecurity.</li>\n  <li>Possess CyberSecurity certifications.</li>\n  <li>Possess Government domain is preferred.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p>\n<p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p>\n<p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
